An Interactive visualization of earthquake data from USGS and GDP
==================================================================


This is an interactive visualization which displays the Earthquakes
happened in the past 1 year according to the magnitude and depth
with different animated markers on the World Map.

The interactivity inculudes:
Click on city marker to find the nearest earthquakes and their average magnitude
Click on earthquake maker to get additional details and nearby airports
Click on any ocean earthquake to display the all the cities potentially being affected
Click on view GDP button to color countries based on their GDP(Red-lowest, dark blue - highest)

